<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Importance of Trees</title>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Importance of Trees</h1>

    <p>
        Trees play a vital role in maintaining the balance of nature. They
        provide oxygen, absorb carbon dioxide, prevent soil erosion, and offer
        shelter to many animals. Planting more trees helps create a healthier
        and greener environment for future generations.
    </p>

</body>
</html>  
